{
  "texts": [
    "In the following sections of this paper, Prompt 4 was used for the investigation.",
    "In this test, we used the best prompt via zero-shot learning from the previous section to test the extraction performance of the three Llama 2 models, i.e., 7B, 13B, and 70B.",
    "Here, Prompt 4 was employed within Llama 2 7B and 13B to extract well location and depth information from the 160 well records.",
    "Subsequently, we compared these extraction results with those from Llama 2 70B model.",
    "Tables 4 5 show the comparison results for Colorado and Pennsylvania cases, respectively."
  ]
}